name: Dream Loving Fellas XVI
description:
The feathered serpent (Quetzalcoatl) represents two spiritual aspects:
- The quetzal is the symbol of the spirit, in that it is the bird with the most beautiful plumage that overcomes gravity and takes flight to the unfathomable heights of the spirit.
- And the serpent is the symbol of matter, inasmuch as it is the reptile, the animal that crawls over the material world and where it exercises its power".

Dambass 2021
